AU.1.1.7 Password Requirements

encrypt password = yes, if smbpasswd option is in use	encrypt password = yes	If smbpasswd option is in use, samba passwords stored on the Samba server must be encrypted, via "encrypt password" in smb.conf.

cat /etc/samba/smb.conf | grep -i encrypt

"por lo que, para poner un NO en la pregunta y generar desviación deberíamos encontrar explícitamente"

"encrypt passwords = no"

