AU.1.8.8.2 Protecting Resources - OSR's

Files/commands/scripts executed on the server via entries in smb.conf.	Each active entry must specify full path of the file/command/script to be executed.	Protection requirements for system facility entries executing with privilege authority.


"Todos los path definidos dentro de smb.conf ,tienen que ser completos"

cat  /etc/samba/smb.conf|grep -i path
